<br>
I guess I was not totally clear in my request, I would not want anyone to have to stay up till 3am to post an intention.  That said, yes, in this case it was me that had to stay up.  I would not take the time to post on someone else's behalf, that should be up to them.  If I lived on the west coast, I would not have a problem, but that does not mean that a problem does not exist.<br>
<br>
I still say that a time could be picked that would be convienent to MOST of the players on Brell.  That time might be Noon Eastern (9am Pacific, 6pm Euopean, not sure Asian time but I think its about Midnight, that would put 3am somewhere in the middle of the Pacific Ocean).<br>
<br>
We do agree on one thing, this is silly (not my post, but posting intentions) and something does need to give pretty soon.<br>
